Subject: [PATCH] use grub2 as a package name

This will ease all of the renaming of directories and all the pkgdata
hacks.

Signed-off-by: Jiri Slaby <jirislaby@gmail.com>
---
 configure    |   24 ++++++++++++------------
 configure.ac |    2 +-
 2 files changed, 13 insertions(+), 13 deletions(-)

Index: grub-2.06/configure.ac
===================================================================
--- grub-2.06.orig/configure.ac
+++ grub-2.06/configure.ac
@@ -34,7 +34,7 @@ dnl "TARGET_" (such as TARGET_CC, TARGET
 dnl the target type. See INSTALL for full list of variables and
 dnl description of the relationships between them.
 
-AC_INIT([GRUB],[2.06],[bug-grub@gnu.org])
+AC_INIT([GRUB2],[2.06],[bug-grub@gnu.org])
 
 AC_CONFIG_AUX_DIR([build-aux])
 
